-- HSBC’s Qu Says Cut Shows China Does What It Takes for Growth
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-06-07T12:00:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/hsbc-s-qu-says-cut-shows-china-does-what-it-takes-for-growth.html
Qu Hongbin, co-head of Asia Economics
at  HSBC Holdings PLC (5) , comments on China’s decision to cut
interest rates for the first time since 2008.  “This move carries a significant message. It is official:
Beijing will do whatever it takes to support growth this year.
So get ready for more decisive easing measures in the coming
months.”  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
